headline: OX Security Appoints Ohad Cohen as Chief Revenue Officer to Accelerate Global Growth
summary: OX, a leader in Application Security, today announced the appointment of Ohad Cohen as Chief Revenue Officer (CRO). In this role, Cohen will oversee global sales operations and go-to-market strategy, furthering OX Security's mission to enable organizations to focus solely on the cyber risks that actually matter, from code to runtime.
